headline.main: HIGH PRICES CUT AID TO NEEDIEST; Public Must Give $40,000 to Reach Last Year's Total-- More for Same Comforts. DAY'S DONATIONS FALL OFF Only $9,259 Received, as Against $13,276 on the Day Before. A CHARITY WITHOUT COSTS Every Cent Given Goes to the Neediest, with No Charge forAdministration.
